          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long before I notice a difference?",
            "answer": "<p>Most people notice meaningful improvement within 3-6 weeks as the metabolic processing pathways restore. Breath-related improvements often come first (3-4 weeks), followed by body odor improvements as the gut barrier strengthens and fewer metabolites enter systemic circulation (4-8 weeks). The timeline varies by individual gut composition and the degree of bacterial depletion.</p>"
